<div class="containerCardInfo">
    <h2>交易紀錄</h2>
    <p>
        已購買課程將無法退回現金，僅能退至AmazingTalker作為消費幣使用，若因為教師或學生個人因素導致無法繼續上課，請點此
        『申請課程退AT幣』
    </p>
    <p>若待付款訂單中包含"未付款之體驗課"，需先取消或支付該筆訂單方可成功購買</p>

    <!-- 訂單資訊 -->
    <h3>訂單資訊</h3>
    <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample">
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#orderId-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="orderId-1">
                    訂單編號 #1
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="orderId-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <div class="order-info">
                        <h5>訂單資料</h5>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-hover table-success-order table-transaction">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>交易時間</td>
                                        <td>教師名稱</td>
                                        <td>課程內容</td>
                                        <td>堂數</td>
                                        <td>金額</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>2024/08/01</td>
                                        <td>Allen</td>
                                        <td>日文課</td>
                                        <td>5堂</td>
                                        <td>NT 500</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reserve-info">
                        <h5>預約資訊</h5>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-hover table-success-order">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>教師名稱</td>
                                        <td>課程內容</td>
                                        <td>預約日期</td>
                                        <td>預約時間</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Allen</td>
                                        <td>日文課</td>
                                        <td>2024/08/01</td>
                                        <td>17:00~18:00 </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional Accordion Items -->
    </div>

    <div class="btn-goback">
        <br>
        <button class="return-order_btn text-white" type="button">返回購物車</button>
    </div>
</div>
